subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Rutgers faces an enormous second-round challenge in Auburn on Monday, a team rested and eager to play a reputable opponent, even if it is on the opponent’s home court.
